---
description: React Hooks best practices for frontend package
globs:
  - "packages/frontend/**"
alwaysApply: true
---
- Always use `useEffect` cleanup functions to avoid memory leaks.
- Prefer `useCallback` and `useMemo` to optimize re-renders.
- Avoid using class components; prefer functional components.
- Avoid excessive use of `useState`; for complex state logic, use `useReducer`.
